modShortDescription: Adds missing textures to the paint tool. There are 10 textures that are present in the game but are not available when painting. This mod makes them available.
modDescription:
Adds missing textures to the paint tool. There are 10 textures that are present in the game but are not available when painting. This mod makes them available.

**[Download](https://github.com/Laotseu/7dtdMods/releases/download/MorePaintTextures_v1.0/MorePaintTextures_v1.0.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19462-motorcyclealterations-v10-alpha-18/).
